Groups & Events in Key Largo
Planning a destination wedding or productive business conference in Key Largo doesn’t have to be stressful. Let Marina Del Mar Resort take the hassle out of finding comfortable, affordable accommodations for your entire entourage. When you book a block of rooms at our Ocean Breeze Inn destination, you can expect easy access to some of the area’s most dreamy wedding locales and world-class meeting facilities so your happily-ever-after or strategic planning session can go off without a hitch.
Drop Us a Line
Start Planning
To learn more about our availability and pricing information for your next Key Largo meeting or event, please request a meeting quote or book your event online.

Groups & Events on Sanibel Island
Headed to Sanibel Island for an upcoming business or social event? Relaxation and comfort await on the sandy shores of the Gulf of Mexico at Sanibel Island Beach Resort. Whether making your way to the coast for a meeting, corporate retreat, wedding, family reunion or something in between, nothing beats a beachfront backdrop to rest and rejuvenate. Our full-service hotel offers everything your group needs for a memorable experience, including comfortable and newly renovated accommodations, on-site dining, an outdoor Tiki Bar and easy access to all the sights and experiences of beautiful Sanibel Island.

Vero Beach business and social events have found a home at Ocean Breeze Inn Vero Beach. Host an inspiring gathering for up to 90 people in our meeting facility spanning 1,448 square feet. With access to free Wi-Fi and audio/visual equipment, you’ll have all of the necessary tools for success at your fingertips. And with a variety of comfortable guest rooms and suites, delicious dining options, and plenty of local attractions to keep your guests entertained in between meetings, Ocean Breeze Inn Vero Beach is the perfect place for your next meeting or event near the water.
A Space to Gather
More About The Venue
Our beachfront hotel is ideal for your next family reunion or social event in Vero Beach. Gather around the fire pit with family, friends, and colleagues.
Event planning services are available.
